articles.author: Ashley Strickland
articles.title: ‘Ring of fire’ eclipse appears over the Americas - CNN
articles.description: An annular solar eclipse created a “ring of fire” in the skies over the Americas Saturday, and millions more saw a crescent-shaped partial solar eclipse.
